textRun.content: Please be sure to check the transportation lists as Hotchkiss facilities are not available Monday and Tuesday to court teams:
Please check emails for edits on your recs and notify Lisa or Emily once you have approved any changes.
If you have not submitted your recs, please contact Lisa with a plan ASAP.
Reminder to be present and accountable during your new duty assignments.
Student travel information will be sent soon via email for closing duty faculty. Please highlight students as they depart.
